(b) Must use **at least three of these dplyr verbs**: group_by, mutate, summarize, select, count, and top_n (or slice_max)

(c) Must use %>% to pipe data manipulation processes. Manipulation and visualization must be chained together using %>%.

(d) Both plots:
- Must have meaningful x-axis and y-axis titles
- Must have an overall meaningful plot title
- Include proper legend tables
- Be well-structured and visually clear
